{"tid":658497,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"特權波　座駕cut入巴士專線　 運輸署拒交代許可證權限","createTime":"2018-05-09T04:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T11:03:54.000Z","uid":12853,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0fcf7d41992ff31d1a554ab806993376a0b690de","tid":658497,"uid":12853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T04:45:27.000Z","msg":"【司長大晒】<br />\n【本報訊】財政司司長陳茂波的紅色專屬座駕再涉及道路違例爭議，周日陳坐着其座駕沿灣仔堅拿道天橋行駛，至一個分岔口時突然切線入巴士專線，再插隊駛回往紅隧的行車線。<br />\n<br />\n財政司司長辦公室回覆指司長座駕獲運輸署發出許可證，可使用巴士專線。有立法會議員批許可證如同特權，促當局公開許可證涵蓋範圍。<br />\n<br />\n市民胡亂駛入可罰$2,000<br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180509/20385159\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180509%2F20385159&d=TSnP4WbJqntNZ1aUBGXHqgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=4bc836f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180509%2F20385159&h=20ee4193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180509/20385159</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ca0399b090c4f75fe66fdc5d97e3ccde6ddb6cad","tid":658497,"uid":63190,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:40:44.000Z","msg":"再嘈下年冇退稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce86123756e0bb11e9c488bafe5d5e7e606fadc","tid":658497,"uid":55924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T11:03:54.000Z","msg":"波叔每犯一次法就升一次職 <br />\n係政職黎"}]}